6. Key Features (MVP Scope)
A. Meeting Listener (AI Agent)
	‚Ä¢	Joins meetings via API (Zoom SDK or Google Meet transcript feed).
	‚Ä¢	Records or transcribes live audio.
	‚Ä¢	Performs speaker diarization (who said what).
	‚Ä¢	Extracts sentences mentioning tickets (e.g., ‚ÄúI finished issue 231‚Äù or ‚ÄúI‚Äôm working on 198‚Äù).
B. Update Parser (NLP Engine)
	‚Ä¢	Uses keyword & pattern recognition to detect:
	‚Ä¢	Issue IDs (#231, ‚Äúissue 231‚Äù, ‚Äúticket 231‚Äù).
	‚Ä¢	Action verbs like completed, working on, fixed, blocked, testing.
	‚Ä¢	Maps each recognized action to a GitLab status transition or comment.
C. GitLab Integrator
	‚Ä¢	Authenticates via GitLab OAuth or PAT (Personal Access Token).
	‚Ä¢	Fetches issue board for a specific project.
	‚Ä¢	Updates ticket status or adds comments automatically.
D. Scrum Summary Generator
	‚Ä¢	After the meeting ends, generates a structured summary:
